OL,3,CDaughter of cyclist killed by driver
OL,4,Cwith poor vision calls for law change
OL,6,FThe family of a cyclist from
OL,7,FHampshire, who was killed by a driver
OL,8,Fwith poor eyesight, are joining calls
OL,9,Ffor a change in the law.
OL,11,FJim Tassell, 70, suffered a fatal head
OL,12,Finjury in July 2021 when he was
OL,13,Fknocked down by an elderly driver who
OL,14,Fdid not meet the legal eyesight
OL,15,Frequirements.
OL,17,FJim, from Andover, was airlifted to
OL,18,FSouthampton General Hospital, but died
OL,19,Ffive days later.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
