OL,3,CDaughter of cyclist killed by driver
OL,4,Cwith poor vision calls for law change
OL,6,FIt was later revealed that the 81-year-
OL,7,Fold driver could only see three metres
OL,8,Fin front of him, instead of the
OL,9,Frequired 20 metres.
OL,11,FHis daughter Emma Damen wants eye
OL,12,Ftests for drivers to be required by
OL,13,Flaw to prevent anyone else going
OL,14,Fthrough what they have.
OL,16,FEmma said: "You're literally playing
OL,17,Fwith somebody's life. If you know your
OL,18,Feyesight is poor, go and get it
OL,19,Fchecked, because if you don't you
OL,20,Fcould do to a family what's happened
OL,21,Fto us.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
