OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F417A1732789660
OL,3,CDaughter of cyclist killed by driver
OL,4,Cwith poor vision calls for law change
OL,6,F"We've been devastated by what's
OL,7,Fhappened to us because somebody made
OL,8,Fthat choice, to continue driving
OL,9,Fknowing that their eyesight was so
OL,10,Fpoor."
OL,12,FCurrently, drivers must be able to
OL,13,Fread a car number plate from 20 metres
OL,14,Faway, with glasses or contact lenses
OL,15,Fif necessary.
OL,17,FHowever, this is only checked at the
OL,18,Fbeginning of the practical driving
OL,19,Ftest and not every time a licence is
OL,20,Frenewed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
