OL,3,CDaughter of cyclist killed by driver
OL,4,Cwith poor vision calls for law change
OL,6,FEmma said: "So at the moment, it's a
OL,7,Ftick box, you tick a box to say 'I'm
OL,8,Ffit and healthy to drive', and that's
OL,9,Fit. There's no checking of that, it is
OL,10,Fa choice, and my dad paid the ultimate
OL,11,Fprice for that choice.
OL,13,F"The thought of this happening to any
OL,14,Fother family just fills me with horror.
OL,16,F"My dad was a true true gentleman, a
OL,17,Freally nice guy. The ultimate family
OL,18,Fguy. He was the best dad."
