OL,6,FThe Association of Optometrists wants
OL,7,Fdrivers to be required to produce
OL,8,Fevidence to prove they meet the legal
OL,9,Feyesight requirements when renewing
OL,10,Ftheir licence.
OL,12,FDrivers must renew their photocard
OL,13,Flicence every 10 years. Anyone over
OL,14,Fthe age of 70, must renew their
OL,15,Flicence every three years.
OL,17,FAdam Sampson, Chief Executive,
OL,18,FAssociation of Optometrists, said:
OL,19,F"This law was introduced in 1938. It's
OL,20,Fnever been revised since.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
