OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F417A1732789660
OL,3,CDaughter of cyclist killed by driver
OL,4,Cwith poor vision calls for law change
OL,6,F"All you've got to do is to
OL,7,Fdemonstrate you can see a number plate
OL,8,Fwhen you're 17 or 18 and you qualify
OL,9,Fto drive.
OL,11,F"After that, you simply self-certify
OL,12,Fto the DVLA, all the way through, that
OL,13,Fyou've still got the eyesight capable
OL,14,Fof seeing.
OL,16,F"We're seeing more and more cases of
OL,17,Fparticularly elderly people with poor
OL,18,Feyesight fatally injuring pedestrians
OL,19,Fand other road users simply because
OL,20,Fthey can't see.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
