OL,3,CDaughter of cyclist killed by driver
OL,4,Cwith poor vision calls for law change
OL,6,F"So we're calling for the law to be
OL,7,Fchanged and requiring people to
OL,8,Fproduce evidence, so when they say
OL,9,Fthey can see, they actually can."
OL,11,FA recent survey by the Association of
OL,12,FOptometrists found that almost six in
OL,13,F10 optometrists have seen a patient in
OL,14,Fthe last month who continues to get
OL,15,Fbehind the wheel, despite their vision
OL,16,Fbeing below the legal standard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
