OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,7,FTransport said: "Every death on our
OL,8,Froads is a tragedy, and our thoughts
OL,9,Fremain with the families of everyone
OL,10,Fwho has lost a loved one in this way.
OL,12,F"The NHS recommends adults should have
OL,13,Ftheir eyes tested every two years, and
OL,14,Fwhile we do not have plans to change
OL,15,Feyesight requirements for driving, we
OL,16,Fcontinue to explore ways to improve
OL,17,Froad safety."
