OL,6,FOn Friday, 2 September 2022 at
OL,7,FSalisbury Crown Court, Peter Gardner
OL,8,Fwas jailed for six months for causing
OL,9,Fdeath by careless driving after
OL,10,Fpleading guilty.
OL,12,FIn his sentencing remarks, the judge
OL,13,Fsaid Gardner must have known his
OL,14,Feyesight was failing.
